<p><b>10.6.&nbsp;&nbsp; Export refunds</b></p><p>The main form of assistance to the EU poultry sector is the provision of export refunds. This provides export refund support for both eggs and poultrymeat. In general, export refund assistance is not provided in support of frozen poultry part exports, which is the main plank of EU–ACP trade in poultry products.</p><p>Table 10.6.1: Appropriations and outturns (in €)</p><table class="renderedtable" border="1" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="0">
